            </h1>

            <div class="infosTabs">
                <h2 class="tab active">
                    <span>
                        <a>How to win?</a>
                    </span>
                </h2>
                <div class="tabContent">
                    <p>
                        <strong>Simply by getting involved!</strong>
                        Each time I submit an idea, I vote, I answer a poll or I win a challenge,
                        <strong>I win and accumulate points.</strong>
                        And when my idea is implemented,
                        <strong>JACKPOT !</strong>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="infosTabs">
                <h2 class="tab active">
                    <span>
                        <a>But Eurêka is also…</a>
                    </span>
