                        …
                        <strong>rewards</strong>
                        for the best ones:
                        <strong>Trophies</strong>
                        (Best contributor award, best innovative idea award…). … many
                        <strong>surprises</strong>
                        and a chance to be involved in a completely new adventure!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="infosTabs">
                <h2 class="tab active">
                    <span>
                        <a>What are the accumulated points for?</a>
                    </span>
                </h2>
                <div class="tabContent">
                    <p>
                        <strong>For buying gifts at the online shop.</strong>
                        The more points I get, the more I can indulge myself.
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        <strong>For becoming the program's super STAR:</strong>
                        the more I participate, the more my status evolve.
                        <strong>There are 5 status, function of the contribution level:</strong>
                        Pioneer, Explorer, Discoverer, Visionary and last, the
                        more active of the community will be proud of holding the Brilliant status.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="infosTabs">
                <h2 class="tab active">
                    <span>
                        <a>When can I convert my points?</a>
                    </span>
                </h2>
                <div class="tabContent">
                    <p>
                        My available points and my acquired points are visible in <strong>My Profile</strong>.<br/>
                        <strong>My available points</strong> correspond to the points I haven't converted to gifts yet.<br/>
                        <strong>My acquired points</strong> correspond to the points I have accumulated since my first connection.<br/>
                        When my available points reach a <strong>500 points level</strong>, I will be able de convert them to gifts
                        at two moments in the year: in <strong>July/August</strong> and in <strong>December/January</strong>.<br/>
                        For better handling of the gifts request and distribution, no request will be processed outside of this 2
                        periods.<br/>
                        In the event of an extended absence (due to prolonged illness, motherhood, training...), my points are
                        kept acquired.<br/>
                        In the event of a company departure, the balance of the available points could be settled upon the
                        salaried request before her departure. The gift delivery will be performed in <strong>July/August or in
                        December/January, function of the distribution agenda</strong>.
                    </p>
                </div>
